3.10	The_Civilization_of_the_Renaissance_in_Italy	The Civilization of the Renaissance in Italy	The Civilization of the Renaissance in Italy is an 1860 work on the Italian Renaissance by Swiss historian Jacob Burckhardt. Together with his History of the Renaissance in Italy (Die Geschichte der Renaissance in Italien; 1867) it is counted among the classics of Renaissance historiography.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/28/Die_Kultur_der_Renaissance_in_Italien_.jpg/260px-Die_Kultur_der_Renaissance_in_Italien_.jpg
